<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ق ل ق ل<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٤٠٨٣ - ق ل ق ل]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قلقلَ يقلقل، قَلْقلَةً، فهو مُقَلْقِل، والمفعول مُقَلْقَل<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• قلقل الحجَرَ:</span> حرَّكه وهزَّه بشدَّة <span class="c1">"قلقل حديثُهم أحزانَهم الكامنة"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• قلقل الحزنُ دمعَهُ:</span> أسالَه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>